# ğŸ“Š Array Analytics Dashboard

A JavaScript mini-app that collects user numbers into an array and calculates **sum, product, and average** once the required number of elements is reached.

## ğŸ“Œ Description
The user first chooses how many numbers to enter.  
As numbers are added:
- A progress bar fills dynamically
- A counter tracks entered values  
When the array is complete, statistics are calculated and displayed.

